Short: GLTron AOS4 source
Type: game/misc
Author: Massimiliano m3x Tretene (glquake@libero.it)

Author of the original 68k/WOS port: Jarmo Laakkonen (jami.laakkonen@kolumbus.fi)

This is the AmigaOS4 port of gltron, a 3d lightcycle game using OpenGL. 

Requires AOS4, Warp3D and AHI.

The original version uses F12 to take screenshots. On Amiga the key is
mapped to HELP instead.

NOTE: fullscreen mode doesn't work. To change window dimension, just edit 
the .gltronrc file
